Try to write the requirements for simple arcade style driving game where the player has to navigate around obstacles to keep from crashing.
Mandatory:
- Display score from present and past player/user
- Create different levels of difficulties for each obstacles
- Create different type of obstacles for the players to navigate
- Create a scoreboard that lists of player that beats each obstacles the from the fastest to slowest
Optional:
- Be able to have multiple players play at the same time.
- Be able to played in different platforms
